room_title: Escape room "Asylum" by Mission Manor in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: So much fun! As a two-person team, we did the Asylum room and made it out in time! It was a blast!

room_title: Escape room "Asylum" by Mission Manor in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: I've never done an escape room before, and after Mission Manor I'm already obsessed. Went in to try out Asylum and had such a good time we all decided to stay and go through Countdown. We will be back for Inheritance!

room_title: Escape room "Asylum" by Mission Manor in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: This was my first ever escape room and I couldn't have been happier to have this be my first. We did Asylum and had so much fun that we stayed and did Countdown right after! The staff was super friendly and our host was amazing. We'll definitely be back to do the third room!
